    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《节奏朋克》是一款自上而下的竞技场射击游戏，玩家扮演一名音乐家，试图通过创作致命的乐曲在一群机器人中生存下来。从各种武器、技能和声音中进行选择，每个选择都会导向不同的乐曲和游戏风格，使得每次游戏过程都是独特的。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/c0b6f32843e5fff3da5cba3f6d5ba8e1.poster.avif?t=1749464475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/c0b6f32843e5fff3da5cba3f6d5ba8e1.webm?t=1749464475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/c0b6f32843e5fff3da5cba3f6d5ba8e1.mp4?t=1749464475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在遥远的未来，人们对音乐娱乐的需求已经发生了变化。人们意识到，只有为了生存而战的音乐家，才能创造出最独特的乐曲。因此，音乐家们与一群杀手机器人展开了殊死搏斗，以证明他们在生存和作曲方面都是精英中的精英。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/33b76937bbe9122ad44258eae4cfd567.poster.avif?t=1749464475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/33b76937bbe9122ad44258eae4cfd567.webm?t=1749464475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/33b76937bbe9122ad44258eae4cfd567.mp4?t=1749464475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会拥有武器化的乐器帮助你对抗一群机器人，以证明你是名副其实的“最佳音乐家”。游戏中一共有8种乐器，16种技能，150多种声音组合，随着你越变越强，这些元素组合出的音乐也会越来越致命。使用不同的技能、声音组合，制作独特的乐曲吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/1e3fbcae0e577d34085e4413cecb6e56.poster.avif?t=1749464475\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/1e3fbcae0e577d34085e4413cecb6e56.webm?t=1749464475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2205610/extras/1e3fbcae0e577d34085e4413cecb6e56.mp4?t=1749464475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
